salary_data <- read.csv("salary_data.csv")

salary_data$Job.Title.Grouped <- fct_lump(salary_data$Job.Title, n = 10)

linear_reg_model_grouped <- lm(Salary ~ Age + Gender + Education.Level +
    Job.Title.Grouped + Years.of.Experience, data = salary_data)

summary(linear_reg_model_grouped)

library(ggplot2)

p_age <- plot_model(linear_reg_model_grouped, type = "pred", terms = "Age") +
    geom_point(data = salary_data, aes(x = Age, y = Salary), color = "blue",
        alpha = 0.5) + theme_minimal()
print(p_age)


p_years.of.experience <- plot_model(linear_reg_model_grouped, type = "pred",
    terms = "Years.of.Experience") + geom_point(data = salary_data, aes(x = Years.of.Experience,
    y = Salary), color = "blue", alpha = 0.5) + theme_minimal()
print(p_years.of.experience)
